title: JCP recommendations on PDP Bill will negatively impact India’s tech ambitions: IAMAI - Economic Times
content: JCP recommendations on PDP Bill will negatively impact India’s tech ambitions: IAMAI  Economic Times
description: IAMAI is of the view that the recommendations are likely to negatively impact a cross section of tech industry segments such as large tech companies, tech services companies as well as digital start-ups who form the backbone of Indias tech leadership aspirations.
